post0.title: Cases in Malaysia
post0.content: COVID-19: Malaysia at a Glance . as of April 15, 2020 12PMConfirmed Cases5,072 . (+85)Deaths83 . 1.64% (+1)Recovered2,647 . 52.19% (+169) _base = alt.Chart(df_closed_my.round(6)[['Date', 'Recovered_Rate', 'Deaths_Rate']]).encode(x='Date:T') _recovered = _base.mark_line(color='green').encode( y=alt.Y('Recovered_Rate:Q', axis=alt.Axis(format='%'))) _deaths = _base.mark_line(color='red').encode(y=alt.Y('Deaths_Rate:Q', axis=alt.Axis(format='%'))) (_recovered + _deaths).properties(title='Outcome of Total Closed Case (Recovery Rate vs Death Rate)', width=600) .
